CHAPTER 4
1 The sons of Judah; Pharez, Hez-
ron, and Carmi, and Hur, and Sho- bal.
2 And Reaiah the son of Shobal be- gat Jahath; and Jahath begat Ahu- mai, and Lahad. These are the fami- lies of the Zorathites.
